# FileUploader

`TxFileUploader` is a controlled file-selection component. It opens the native file picker, accepts drag-and-drop files, emits normalized file records, and renders a removable selected-file list.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/file-uploader/src/types.ts`, `TxFileUploader.vue`, and `file-uploader.test.ts`.

